# Loomin Physics Sandbox — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your keys

# ─── AI Models ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# NVIDIA NIM API key (primary — for nemotron-ultra-253b thinking + nemotron-nano-8b fast)
# Get yours at https://ngc.nvidia.com → API Keys
NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-...

# Groq API key (fallback if NVIDIA_API_KEY is not set — llama-3.3-70b + llama-3.1-8b)
# Get yours at https://console.groq.com
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# ─── Model routing ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Thinking (HQ) model: nvidia/llama-3.1-nemotron-ultra-253b-v1  OR  llama-3.3-70b-versatile
# Fast model:          nvidia/llama-3.1-nemotron-nano-8b-v1     OR  llama-3.1-8b-instant
# The app auto-selects NVIDIA if NVIDIA_API_KEY is present, otherwise uses Groq.
